dolls.name: オルク
dolls.description: Flying enemy capable of long-distance attacks. Switches to a tentacle form when at low health

dolls.name: ネクス・エアリオ
dolls.description: Believed to be a mistake in the Global version. Appears in the Japanese Version as "Nex Aelio"

dolls.name: ダイダル・ソード
dolls.description: Giant DOLLS enemy. Can be knocked down by attacking their feet, making it easier to attack the weakpoint on its chest.

dolls.name: ブジン
dolls.description: A small DOLLS boss enemy with quick, ninja-like attacks. Attacks with clones once its HP is low.

alters.name: ワウロン
alters.description: Has kicks that sends out shockwaves.

formers.name: アードバンシー
formers.description: Resembles a Fang Banshee Sylvant from PSO2. Can attack at long-range with wind attacks.

formers.name: アードバンサー
formers.description: Resembles a Fang Banser Sylvant from PSO2. Attacks with zan-like (wind) attacks.

formers.name: クラッグベア
formers.description: Resembles the Rockbear Sylvant from PSO2. Can create shockwaves from punching the ground as well as grabbing players midair
